    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Solid fair-condition driver that appears complete and usable, but it is not a show car. Expect visible age and wear throughout, including cosmetic flaws in the paint and trim, an older interior with use showing, and the possibility of some deferred maintenance or sorting typical of an older car. That said, it presents as a car you can enjoy while improving over time rather than a full project. A straightforward, honest example for someone who wants a driver-grade car at a realistic price.",
