    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, budget-friendly ride with plenty of life and character left? This one has been a dependable car and would make a great daily driver, commuter, or first car for someone who wants good value without spending a fortune. It\u2019s in fair condition, so it shows the normal signs of age and use, but it\u2019s still a practical, honest vehicle that\u2019s ready to be appreciated by its next owner. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want something straightforward and affordable.",
      "price": 18950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Well-kept driver with solid mechanical feel and plenty of life left. The engine pulls cleanly, transmission shifts as it should, and the chassis feels composed on the road. Fair-condition cosmetics with the expected wear for its age, but it presents honestly and has clearly been used and maintained as a dependable car rather than neglected. A great option for someone who wants a capable, enjoyable vehicle at a sensible price.",
