    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn charm that makes every drive feel a little more grounded and memorable. It\u2019s a practical, stylish option for someone who wants dependable transportation with real personality\u2014equally at home on a daily commute, weekend errands, or as a budget-friendly stepping stone into ownership. The cabin offers a comfortable, lived-in feel, and the overall presence still turns heads in that understated way that says it has stories left to tell. If you\u2019re looking for value, character, and a vehicle that invites you to make it your own, this one is easy to appreciate.",
      "price": 21950.0,
